- import libs accordingly
- they dont mark how you code, they mark the output only with respect to the required input shape
- set epoch to 10-20 for image classification problems and early callback patient to 3-5 so we know if our model is not performing well and fine-tune it
- if you have to retrain the model, comment out the dataset downloading part to avoid redownloading
